{"tid":691922,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"重裝Avast，nb電池竟然可用多一倍！","createTime":"2018-06-06T07:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T07:03:04.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5751e5bd685e6b359fbff1c506a695671da68b","tid":691922,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"真係好匪夷所思！<br />\n<br />\n我有部陳年nb，叉滿電，都只可以用到三個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n前幾日屎忽痕，剷左原先個Avast，重裝返兩年前既Avast ver. 11。<br />\n<br />\n神奇既事情發生啦！<br />\n<br />\n我照用三個鐘，仲淨底4x%電力！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87413edf76cdd45cacdb46442730d4156a0bed51","tid":691922,"uid":35507,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"剷埋avast應該再多一倍"},{"pid":"e0da72ca7626941c48524dc117a845ad3874bf98","tid":691922,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剷埋avast應該再多一倍</blockquote><br />\n我都以為係。試過唔得"},{"pid":"c0db5994035d6bc703043ef5db9e75ae34aea4c6","tid":691922,"uid":40421,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"防毒你裝兩年前嘅，同冇裝有咩分別，就算個db有新病毒資料都唔識做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae56d61d0f226eeda15b51d6c48214177df8ef","tid":691922,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"試過裝卡巴斯基用得兩三個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩堂連堂純掛機都用曬啲電"},{"pid":"286458997ea4b97f4e7bf4906e1fd972511d24d9","tid":691922,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>防毒你裝兩年前嘅，同冇裝有咩分別，就算個db有新病毒資料都唔識做野&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n唔係db新就夠？"},{"pid":"d123d